Show list of channels

This command lets you list and search for channels in the currently active radio
network.

Usage:
  radio channels [SEARCH --info]
  radio channels --help

Options:
  -i --info
    Show results with additional info, such as channel description and related
    channels

  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  SEARCH
    Channel name or a partial name to search for

Examples:
  radio channels
  radio channels --info
  radio channels metal
  radio channels metal -i
